<%= image_tag "home1.jpg", class: "Image_home" %>
<div class="Home_container">
  <div class="Home_window">  
    <section class="Home_description">
      <p>
        Welcome to Social Boost, a proof of concept Ruby on Rails app 
        where the users can:
      </p>
      <br />
      <ul>
        <li>Sign up</li>
        <li>Will receive a confirmation email (no action required)</li>
        <li>Log in (only email required for simplicity)</li>
        <li>Create events</li>
        <li>Keep track of past and upcoming events</li>
        <li>Only the creator, attending or invited users can see events</li>
        <li>The creator of the event can invite other registered users</li>
      </ul>
      <br />
      <p>
        <a href=<%= signup_path %>>Create your own user</a> 
        or use the examples to <a href=<%= login_path %>> log in</a>:
      </p>
      <br />
      <ul>
        <li>example1@mail.com (User1)</li>
        <li>example2@mail.com (User2)</li>
      </ul> 
    </section>
  </div>
</div> 
